IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User northcode.no@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg -d --no-tty -q ~/.authinfo.gpg | grep machine imap.gmail.com | cut -d ' ' -f 8"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.mail/gmail/Inbox
SubFolders verbatim

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
MaxMessages 0
Patterns * ![Gmail]* "[Gmail]/All Mail" "[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Create Both
Remove Both
Sync All
SyncState *

IMAPAccount northcode
Host northcode.no
User andreas@northcode.no
PassCmd "gpg -d --no-tty -q ~/.authinfo.gpg | grep login andreas@northcode.no | cut -d ' ' -f 8"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore northcode-remote
Account northcode

MaildirStore northcode-local
Path ~/.mail/northcode/
Inbox ~/.mail/northcode/Inbox
SubFolders verbatim

Channel northcode
Master :northcode-remote:
Slave :northcode-local:
MaxMessages 0
Patterns * 
Create Both
Remove Both
Sync All
SyncState *